    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Implements for cutting dough, having a rotating wheel with a fluted, jagged, toothed, or otherwise shaped edge; used to cut, crimp, or decorate pastry or dough.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
